trans-unit.source: Encapsulates the collection of <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Image" /> objects in an <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.
This is used to manage the images in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> programmatically, providing methods to add and remove image objects.
trans-unit.target: 에 있는 이미지를 관리 하는 데는이 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> 프로그래밍 방식으로 추가 이미지 개체를 제거 하는 메서드를 제공 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to select, remove, and display images, from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> class, which is an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageCollection> type.
trans-unit.target: 다음 코드 예제에서는 선택, 제거 및에서 이미지를 표시 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> 속성은 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList> 클래스 즉는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageCollection> 유형입니다.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified object to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.
An <see cref="T:System.Drawing.Icon" /> to add to the list.
Adds the specified icon to the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList" />.
The <xref:System.Drawing.Icon> is converted to a <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> before it is added to the list.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Drawing.Icon> 변환 되는 <xref:System.Drawing.Bitmap> 목록에 추가 되기 전에 합니다.

trans-unit.source: The following code example demonstrates constructing an <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.%23ctor%2A>, adding images to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> property, setting the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageSize%2A> property, and using the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Draw%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 다음 코드 예제에서는 생성 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.%23ctor%2A>, 이미지에 추가 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Images%2A> 속성을 설정는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.ImageSize%2A> 속성을 사용 하는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.ImageList.Draw%2A> 메서드.

trans-unit.source: To run this example, place it in a form that contains a button named `Button1`.
trans-unit.target: 이 예제를 실행 하려면 이라는 버튼을 포함 하는 폼에 배치 `Button1`합니다.

trans-unit.source: The example assumes the existence of FeatherTexture.bmp and Gone Fishing.bmp at c:\Windows\\.
trans-unit.target: 이 예에서는 가정 FeatherTexture.bmp 및 Gone Fishing.bmp c:\Windows에 있음을\\합니다.

trans-unit.source: Change the example accordingly if the bitmaps do not exist on your system or exist at another location.
